	<h2>PRIVACY POLICY</h2>
	<h3>PURPOSE</h3>
	<p>Vichy Singapore has adopted this Privacy Statement in order to inform you of its policies with respect to information collected from this page. Your use of this page constitutes your acceptance of this Privacy Statement and your consent to the practices it describes.</p>
	<h3>PERSONALLY IDENTIFIABLE INFORMATION</h3>
	<p>Personally Identifiable Information is any information that concerns you individually and would permit someone to contact you, for example, your name, address, telephone/fax number, NRIC, email address or any information you submit to Vichy Singapore Facebook that identifies you individually.</p>
	<p>Vichy Singapore Facebook will not collect any personally identifiable information about you unless you provide it. Therefore, if you do not want Vichy Singapore Facebook to obtain any personally identifiable information about you, do not submit it.</p>
	<p>You can visit and browse the Vichy Singapore Facebook without revealing personally identifiable information about yourself. You may also choose to disclose personally identifiable information about yourself, which may be maintained as described below :</p>
	<p>Email and other voluntary communications - You may choose to communicate with Vichy Singapore Facebook through email, via our website, by telephone, in writing, or through other means. We collect the information in these communications, and such information may be personally identifiable. </p>
	<h3>INFORMATION USE</h3>
	<p>Vichy Singapore may use the personally identifiable information collected through Facebook primarily for such purposes as:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Helping to establish and verify the identity of users; </li>
		<li>Processing and sending related communications; </li>
		<li>Providing services and support to users;  </li>
		<li>Improving the page, including tailoring it to users' preferences; </li>
		<li>Providing users with product or service updates, promotional notices and offers, and other information about Vichy; </li>
		<li>Responding to your questions inquiries, comments and instructions; </li>
	</ul>
	
	<h3>DISCLOSURE OF INFORMATION</h3>
	<p>Vichy Singapore Facebook does not provide personally identifiable information to unaffiliated third parties for their use in marketing directly to you. Vichy Singapore Facebook may use unaffiliated companies to help it maintain and operate its page or for other reasons related to the operation of its business, and those companies may receive your personally identifiable information for that purpose. Vichy Singapore Facebook may also disclose personally identifiable information about you in connection with legal requirements, such as in response to an authorized subpoena, governmental request or investigation, or as otherwise permitted by law. Finally, as Vichy Singapore’s business develops, it may sell or buy corporate assets, and in such transactions customer information may be one of the transferred business assets. If Vichy Singapore, its internet businesses, or substantially all of its assets, is acquired, customer information may be one of the assets transferred.</p>
	
	<h3>"COOKIES" AND ADVERTISERS</h3>
	<p>The Vichy Singapore Facebook server, or the servers of companies that are used to operate this site, may place a "cookie" on your computer in order to allow you to use the site and to personalize your experience.</p>
	<p>A "cookie" is a small piece of data that can be sent by a web server to your computer, which then may be stored by your browser on your computer's hard drive. Cookies allow Vichy Singapore to recognize your computer while you are on its site and help customize your online experience and make it more convenient for you. Cookies are also useful in allowing more efficient log-in for users, tracking transaction histories and preserving information between sessions. The information collected from cookies may also be used to improve the functionality of the site.</p>
	
	<h3>EXTERNAL LINKS</h3>
	<p>The Vichy Singapore Facebook page may contain links to other websites, including those of advertisers or third party content providers who offer downloads on Vichy Singapore. Please be aware that Vichy Singapore is not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of other websites. Websites that are accessible by hyperlinks from the Vichy Singapore site may use cookies [link to "Cookies" section]. Vichy Singapore encourages you to read the privacy statements provided by other websites before you provide personally identifiable information to them.</p>
	
